snippet.title: Brutal Doom v21 Gold Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Brutal Doom v21 Gold was released on May 17 2019,  but I only had the time to make a trailer for it just now.

Download: https://www.moddb.com/mods/brutal-doom/downloads
Support me on https://www.patreon.com/sgtmarkiv

Songs by Andrew Hulshult:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_3NSe4EBvX8&ab_channel=AndrewHulshult
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mGlER_aPFkA&ab_channel=AndrewHulshult

Stock transition sounds provided by MrSnooze https://youtu.be/1RavoGSfE3U
